public abstract class AbstractBinaryDataMergeInhibitor
extends AbstractMergeInhibitor
implements BinaryDataIntegrityCheck

Abstract implementation of a MergeInhibitor that is also a BinaryDataIntegrityCheck. This should be the superclass for such checks as MGV_K.

MEME Group
